Package: WaveletCompMod
Version: 1.1.1
Date: 2025-03-25
Title: Computational Wavelet Analysis with Enhanced Padding Methods
Author: Angi Roesch [aut], Harald Schmidbauer [aut], Jonas Dominy [aut, cre]
Description: A modified version of the WaveletComp package for wavelet analysis and reconstruction of time series, cross-wavelets, and phase-difference analysis. This version adds additional padding methods, including MATLAB-style reflection and combined reflection-zero padding, to improve wavelet transform accuracy.
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
License: GPL-2
NeedsCompilation: no
Repository: GitHub
URL: https://github.com/dominyj/WaveletCompMod
